      <title>石油管道破裂可能导致南苏丹暴力和经济崩溃</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-16/burst-oil-pipeline-risks-south-sudan-violence-economic-meltdown</link>
      <description><![CDATA[国际危机组织表示，南苏丹约三分之二原油产量的出口管道破裂，如果不紧急修复，可能会增加这个世界上最年轻的国家重新爆发战斗的风险。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-16/burst-oil-pipeline-risks-south-sudan-violence-economic-meltdown</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 16 May 2024 14:45:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
